{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act17side", "eventName": "愚人號", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "SN-1", "avgTag": "行動前", "storyName": "中心廣場", "storyInfo": "一隻死去的恐魚仍在試圖觀察這片大地。而每一位被觀察者都意識到，格蘭法洛已經陷入了某種巨大的危機。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_ibchurch", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$tech_intro", "key": "$tech_loop", "fadetime": 3.0, "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_450_1#6$1", "name2": "npc_2004_Alty", "fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_450_1#6$1", "name2": "npc_2004_Alty", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "Alty小姐！那首《著魔的重構》我真的非常喜歡！", "name": "極境"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_450_1#6$1"}, {"id": 12, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_450_1#6$1", "name2": "npc_2004_Alty", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是嗎？這我倒沒想到，我以為在薩爾貢雨林隨便想到的點子太過先鋒了來著。", "name": "Alty"}, "figure_art": "npc_2004_Alty"}, {"id": 14, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過原來那個醫生有你這樣的手下？我還以為你們都和她一樣無趣。", "name": "Alty"}, "figure_art": "npc_2004_Alty"}, {"id": 15, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_450_1#1$1", "name2": "npc_2004_Alty", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈......其他幾位呢？", "name": "極境"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_450_1#1$1"}, {"id": 17, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_450_1#1$1", "name2": "npc_2004_Alty", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "Dan跑到海邊去了，她比較興奮。Aya和Frost去了我們落腳的地方，雖然很破敗，但看上去很有趣。", "name": "Alty"}, "figure_art": "npc_2004_Alty"}, {"id": 19, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_450_1#1$1", "name2": "npc_2004_Alty", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有趣......嗎？", "name": "極境"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_450_1#1$1"}, {"id": 21, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_450_1#1$1", "name2": "npc_2004_Alty", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "凱爾希有和你說我們的事情嗎？", "name": "Alty"}, "figure_art": "npc_2004_Alty"}, {"id": 23, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_450_1#1$1", "name2": "npc_2004_Alty", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只是略有耳聞。似乎有什麼重要的東西在各位手上。", "name": "極境"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_450_1#1$1"}, {"id": 25, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聽說大名鼎鼎的日落即逝竟然私下與凱爾希醫生有來往的時候，我真是吃了一驚......", "name": "極境"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_450_1#1$1"}, {"id": 26, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_450_1#1$1", "name2": "npc_2004_Alty", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "說實話，我也吃了一驚。", "name": "Alty"}, "figure_art": "npc_2004_Alty"}, {"id": 28, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過......我很高興這裡有我們的粉絲喔，感覺讓這趟旅程多了點新意。", "name": "Alty"}, "figure_art": "npc_2004_Alty"}, {"id": 29, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_450_1#6$1", "name2": "npc_2004_Alty", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_paper2", "delay": 1.0}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "見到各位，感覺這一個月來遭的罪就都回本了。啊，麻煩您給這張海報也簽個名......", "name": "極境"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_450_1#6$1"}, {"id": 32, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_450_1#6$1", "name2": "npc_2004_Alty", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......你啊，是抱著什麼心情回到伊比利亞的？", "name": "Alty"}, "figure_art": "npc_2004_Alty"}, {"id": 34, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_450_1#1$1", "name2": "npc_2004_Alty", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "說起來稍微有點複雜，而我更沒想到會被日落即逝的Alty問起這個問題。", "name": "極境"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_450_1#1$1"}, {"id": 36, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_450_1#1$1", "name2": "npc_2004_Alty", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你喜歡我們的樂隊名嗎？", "name": "Alty"}, "figure_art": "npc_2004_Alty"}, {"id": 38, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_450_1#6$1", "name2": "npc_2004_Alty", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "簡直稱得上熱愛。", "name": "極境"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_450_1#6$1"}, {"id": 40, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_450_1#6$1", "name2": "npc_2004_Alty", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "謝謝。", "name": "Alty"}, "figure_art": "npc_2004_Alty"}, {"id": 42, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她在哪裡？我以為她會在這裡等著，擺出那種“我什麼都知道”的表情，然後什麼都不告訴我們。", "name": "Alty"}, "figure_art": "npc_2004_Alty"}, {"id": 43, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_450_1#1$1", "name2": "npc_2004_Alty", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我還在等凱爾希醫生的聯絡。她應當不會比你們晚抵達太多。", "name": "極境"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_450_1#1$1"}, {"id": 45, "prop": "StopMusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 3.0}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_450_1#1$1", "name2": "npc_2004_Alty", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但願她能快些......要漲潮了。", "name": "Alty"}, "figure_art": "npc_2004_Alty"}, {"id": 48, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.6}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_ibindoor", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$darkness02_intro", "key": "$darkness02_loop", "fadetime": 3.0, "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_459_1#1$1", "name2": "char_empty", "fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.6}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......外來者。都是外來者。這段時間是怎麼了，難道審判庭真的放鬆警惕到了這個地步？", "name": "男性鎮民"}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_459_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_453_1#1$1", "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_459_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_453_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是的，外人，都是外人。她們都很特殊，身上有海的氣息。", "name": "詭異的教徒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_453_1#1$1"}, {"id": 65, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_459_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_453_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿戈爾人？", "name": "男性鎮民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_459_1#1$1"}, {"id": 67, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_459_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_453_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "像是，可又不是，我們的兄弟姐妹都感到恐懼。", "name": "詭異的教徒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_453_1#1$1"}, {"id": 69, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們必須抓緊，審判庭極少如此疏忽......太可疑了，可哪怕現在這片海域的鬆懈是審判庭的陷阱，我們也必須義無反顧。", "name": "詭異的教徒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_453_1#1$1"}, {"id": 70, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為了幫助我們的兄弟姐妹，為了重建使者與陸地的聯繫，我們必須先一步奪得伊比利亞之眼的控制權......或者是摧毀它！", "name": "詭異的教徒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_453_1#1$1"}, {"id": 71, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不願意濫殺無辜，你們也曾是我的家人。", "name": "詭異的教徒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_453_1#1$1"}, {"id": 72, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_459_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_453_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "男性鎮民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_459_1#1$1"}, {"id": 74, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_459_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_453_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "去讓更多的人加入我們吧，我們有一條更寬闊的道路可以選擇，遠勝伊比利亞許諾的一切，更勝過這片大地。", "name": "詭異的教徒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_453_1#1$1"}, {"id": 76, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_459_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_453_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那些......我們的兄弟們，它們躁動不安，是因為那些外來者？", "name": "男性鎮民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_459_1#1$1"}, {"id": 78, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_459_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_453_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "很可能，但還不確定，我們都很弱小，兄弟姐妹們都很弱小，不能輕舉妄動，審判庭會殺光我們。", "name": "詭異的教徒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_453_1#1$1"}, {"id": 80, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們得......謹慎......否則會在陸上流太多的血，她不喜歡流血......無論是我們，還是我們的兄弟姐妹，都沒必要枉死。", "name": "詭異的教徒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_453_1#1$1"}, {"id": 81, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "MusicVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.1, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_chess"}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.6}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......！誰？！", "name": "詭異的教徒"}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.3, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 8.0, "ystrength": 6.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.5, "r": 1.0, "g": 1.0, "b": 1.0, "fadetime": 0.02, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$swordtsing6", "delay": 0.5}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$swordtsing4"}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.6}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 58.0, "ystrength": 56.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$bodyfalldown2", "volume": 0.5}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_doorbreak", "volume": 0.5}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.6}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_450_1#1$1", "name2": "npc_2004_Alty"}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_ibchurch", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "MusicVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.4, "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_450_1#1$1", "name2": "npc_2004_Alty", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我就知道。邪教徒，深海教徒......最近這些年我都沒來過伊比利亞了，到處都是這種氣息。", "name": "Alty"}, "figure_art": "npc_2004_Alty"}, {"id": 107, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯......不過我開始期待再和她見面了。她還沒來嗎？", "name": "Alty"}, "figure_art": "npc_2004_Alty"}, {"id": 108, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_450_1#1$1", "name2": "npc_2004_Alty", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是的。凱爾希醫生交代過，她極可能會遭到審判庭的監視，所以......", "name": "極境"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_450_1#1$1"}, {"id": 110, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_450_1#1$1", "name2": "npc_2004_Alty", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "奇怪。她應該是看著伊比利亞崛起的，她怎麼會沒有辦法找到他們的頭兒？何必要用這麼粗劣的方式？", "name": "Alty"}, "figure_art": "npc_2004_Alty"}, {"id": 112, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_450_1#6$1", "name2": "npc_2004_Alty", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈，伊比利亞的崛起都是好幾百年前的事情了，就算是凱爾希醫生......", "name": "極境"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_450_1#6$1"}, {"id": 114, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_450_1#6$1", "name2": "npc_2004_Alty", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看來她這些年的經歷還是讓她學會了一些處世之道......唉，不是很懂，畢竟我很年輕嘛。", "name": "Alty"}, "figure_art": "npc_2004_Alty"}, {"id": 116, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_450_1#6$1", "name2": "npc_2004_Alty", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈，Alty小姐說笑了......", "name": "極境"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_450_1#6$1"}, {"id": 118, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_450_1#1$1", "name2": "npc_2004_Alty", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......凱爾希醫生如果真出了什麼意外，你會幫她吧？", "name": "極境"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_450_1#1$1"}, {"id": 120, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_450_1#1$1", "name2": "npc_2004_Alty", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯......如果你替她求情的話。", "name": "Alty"}, "figure_art": "npc_2004_Alty"}, {"id": 122, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她對你們那個，羅德島，對，這麼重要？", "name": "Alty"}, "figure_art": "npc_2004_Alty"}, {"id": 123, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_450_1#1$1", "name2": "npc_2004_Alty", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......說實話啊。我其實不太能理解凱爾希醫生為什麼願意冒著這樣的風險來到伊比利亞。", "name": "極境"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_450_1#1$1"}, {"id": 125, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_450_1#11$1", "name2": "npc_2004_Alty", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但我相信，這是凱爾希醫生自己選擇的職責。而既然連凱爾希醫生都願意為伊比利亞而冒險，更別談我這樣的伊比利亞人了。", "name": "極境"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_450_1#11$1"}, {"id": 127, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_450_1#11$1", "name2": "npc_2004_Alty", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......原來如此。", "name": "Alty"}, "figure_art": "npc_2004_Alty"}, {"id": 129, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那你最好出去看看。或者在這裡等一會也行，應該馬上就會有人衝進來大呼小叫。", "name": "Alty"}, "figure_art": "npc_2004_Alty"}, {"id": 130, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_450_1#11$1", "name2": "npc_2004_Alty", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呃，什麼意思——", "name": "極境"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_450_1#11$1"}, {"id": 132, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$doorclosequite"}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$dooropenquite", "delay": 0.2}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_450_1#5$1", "name2": "npc_2004_Alty"}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 50.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.6}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_460_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們在廣場上——看見了——怪物！有怪物！有人嗎？！", "name": "慌張的鎮民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_460_1#1$1"}, {"id": 141, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$jealous_intro", "key": "$jealous_loop", "fadetime": 2.0, "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_450_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——！Alty小姐，麻煩您待在這裡，我去確認一下！", "name": "極境"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_450_1#7$1"}, {"id": 144, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral", "loop": "true", "channel": "bgs"}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.6}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "bgs", "fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.6}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "npc_2004_Alty", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.6}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......真難聞。", "name": "Alty"}, "figure_art": "npc_2004_Alty"}, {"id": 153, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過Dan說得沒錯，腦海裡的花朵落入逆流的瀑布、鱗片的旋律、根莖的歌謠......都呼之欲出。", "name": "Alty"}, "figure_art": "npc_2004_Alty"}, {"id": 154, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也許這趟旅程後，真的會有不錯的點子。", "name": "Alty"}, "figure_art": "npc_2004_Alty"}, {"id": 155, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.6}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "27_g18_lighthouse_square", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那是......什麼東西......", "name": "圍觀的群眾"}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老佩德里說的沒錯......我在祖父的日記本裡見過這個東西！這就是海怪！", "name": "圍觀的群眾"}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可它......可它死了嗎？它不會動？", "name": "圍觀的群眾"}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 17.0, "ystrength": 15.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_450_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "抱歉，讓一讓，讓一讓——", "name": "極境"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_450_1#7$1"}, {"id": 168, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_450_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——", "name": "極境"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_450_1#5$1"}, {"id": 170, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_457_1#2$1", "fadetime": 1.5, "focus": 3.0}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.6}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "僅存的光芒透過雲層，被燈塔的雕像剝奪了部分軀體。光的血灑在地上，成為陰影。"}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一隻瀕死的恐魚，靜靜躺在雕塑的陰影下，像垂暮的老人倚樹而眠。"}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_457_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "瀕死的恐魚"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_457_1#2$1"}, {"id": 178, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "............", "name": "瀕死的恐魚"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_457_1#2$1"}, {"id": 179, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_450_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......已經......死了嗎？", "name": "極境"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_450_1#2$1"}, {"id": 181, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_460_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老佩德里果然沒說謊！真的是怪物，海裡的怪物，海裡的怪物出現在了格蘭法洛......！", "name": "慌張的鎮民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_460_1#1$1"}, {"id": 183, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我知道它叫什麼，以前我們就見過！", "name": "慌張的鎮民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_460_1#1$1"}, {"id": 184, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_450_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（這就是恐魚？）", "name": "極境"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_450_1#2$1"}, {"id": 186, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_450_1#12$1"}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（可是海岸明明十分平靜，而且審判庭怎麼會放過這麼明顯的......）", "name": "極境"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_450_1#12$1"}, {"id": 188, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_457_1#2$1", "focus": 3.0}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "它了無生氣的眼眸似乎還在環視四周，陸地於它如同乾燥的海洋。"}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_457_1#1$1", "focus": 3.0}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可當極境誤以為它一息尚存時，它的目光又彷彿看向了深邃的死亡，一動不動。"}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_450_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（它......盯著我？還是，盯著什麼......）", "name": "極境"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_450_1#5$1"}, {"id": 196, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 17.0, "ystrength": 15.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "誰來處理一下這具屍體！", "name": "圍觀的群眾"}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看它的樣子，真噁心，如果它活著，它有多可怕，它會吃人嗎？", "name": "圍觀的群眾"}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_457_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "瀕死的恐魚"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_457_1#2$1"}, {"id": 202, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_457_1#2$1", "focus": 3.0}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "恐魚不會說話，畸形的外殼熠熠生輝。"}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一大群人圍在它的周圍。恐懼，質疑，卻都被它吸引，就像點燃的煙火。"}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "煙火，對，它的死亡就像是煙火。看不見傷痕或是手炮留下的彈孔。"}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不是死亡選擇了它，是它選擇了死亡。"}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_450_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......不。我在胡思亂想些什麼。", "name": "極境"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_450_1#9$1"}, {"id": 209, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_450_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果這就是報告裡提到過的恐魚......那麼深海教會確實比想像中更接近這裡。", "name": "極境"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_450_1#2$1"}, {"id": 211, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿瑪雅小姐！您快看看這是什麼東西——", "name": "圍觀的群眾"}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_449_1#9$1", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "先別慌張......", "name": "阿瑪雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_449_1#9$1"}, {"id": 218, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_460_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿瑪雅小姐，這難道就是......海裡的......", "name": "慌張的鎮民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_460_1#1$1"}, {"id": 220, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_449_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不能欺騙大家。是的，這就是......海裡的怪物。", "name": "阿瑪雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_449_1#4$1"}, {"id": 222, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_460_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那、那麼！這件事得快點告訴審判庭！這裡出現了怪物，讓懲戒軍來——不，讓審判官來！", "name": "慌張的鎮民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_460_1#1$1"}, {"id": 224, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 17.0, "ystrength": 15.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "否則我們都會完蛋！", "name": "慌張的鎮民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_460_1#1$1"}, {"id": 226, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "27_g16_lighthouse_street", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.6}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral", "loop": "true", "channel": "bgs", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_460_1#1$1", "fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "middle", "type": "move", "xpos": 400.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_461_1#1$1", "fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "middle", "type": "move", "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "middle", "type": "move", "xpos": 400.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "bgs", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4042_lumen_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_451_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0, "fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "感覺大家都在往禮拜堂的方向跑？", "name": "喬迪"}, "figure_art": "avg_4042_lumen_1#1$1"}, {"id": 251, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_empty", "name2": "char_empty"}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_460_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_451_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "left", "type": "move", "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "left", "type": "move", "xpos": 200.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "right", "type": "move", "xpos": 200.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "right", "type": "move", "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_460_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_451_1#7$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎麼了，喂，發生什麼了？",